results.name: Cubes which do not have a partition as the sum of 2 squares.
formula: Equals A000578 INTERSECT A022544. - _R. J. Mathar_, Nov 23 2006
program: (PARI) isA125111(ncube)={ local(a) ; a=0; while(a^2<=ncube, if(issquare(ncube-a^2), return(0) ; ) ; a++ ; ) ; return(1) ; } { for(n=0,200, if(isA125111(n^3), print1(n^3,",") ; ) ; ) ; } - _R. J. Mathar_, Nov 23 2006
